le><thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>children</code></td><td><code>string</code></td><td>-</td><td>Markdown content to render</td></tr><tr><td><code>components</code></td><td><code>Partial&lt;Components&gt;</code></td><td>-</td><td>Custom <code>react-markdown</code> component overrides</td></tr><tr><td><code>id</code></td><td><code>string</code></td><td>generated</td><td>Stable id seed used for memoized block keys</td></tr><tr><td><code>className</code></td><td><code>string</code></td><td>-</td><td>Additional CSS class</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Also supports all native <code>div</code> HTML attributes.</p></div><div class=\"@container my-8 grid gap-4 grid-cols-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-fd-accent-foreground hover:bg-surface-secondary @max-lg:col-span-full flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-2xl p-4 text-sm transition-none\" href=\"/docs/react/components/code-block\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"-mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M10.53 2.97a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06L6.56 8l3.97 3.97a.75.75 0 1 1-1.06 1.06l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.06l4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg><p>Code Block</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">Syntax-highlighted code blocks with language labels and copy actions for AI markdown.</p></a><a class=\"hover:text-fd-accent-foreground hover:bg-surface-secondary @max-lg:col-span-full flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-2xl p-4 text-sm transition-none text-end\" href=\"/docs/react/components/prompt-input\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium flex-row-reverse\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"-mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M5.47 13.03a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.06L9.44 8 5.47 4.03a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l4.5 4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-4.5 4.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg><p>Prompt Input</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">A composable AI prompt composer with attachments, toolbar actions, send states, queued prompts, and drag-and-drop support.</p></a></div>"}], "tocHtml": "<a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#usage\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Usage</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#streaming\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Streaming</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#with-streamdown\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">With Streamdown</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#anatomy\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Anatomy</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#css-classes\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">CSS Classes</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#base-classes\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">Base Classes</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#element-classes\" class=\"p